{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a90ae50d78","title":"中央转发北京市委关于统战会议情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b8e75f942","index":0,"year":1951,"month":7,"day":6,"articleId":"a90ae50d78"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fc4ed92cc5","type":"title","text":"中央转发北京市委关于统战会议情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a90ae50d78"},{"id":"c41b73b7b7","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a90ae50d78"},{"id":"478a595e93","type":"paragraph","text":"此件很好，发各中央局，并转分局，省市区党委参考，并请仿照办理，加强全党的统一战线工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a90ae50d78"},{"id":"fc9297da77","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央七月六日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a90ae50d78"}],"page":{"id":"b0d95c4c9f","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a90ae50d78","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"91d9560b03","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a90ae50d78","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共北京市委1951年7月5日关于市委统战部召开统战工作会议情况给中央、华北局并报中央、华北局统战部的报告。报告说，这次会议的收获，主要有：1.使干部认识了在新环境下各界民主人士的积极作用和进步的可能性，并批判了以往存在着的对他们估计不足，武断片面肯定他们落后不会进步的错误思想。2.纠正了对客界民主人士不敢领导和怕麻烦的思想。3.解决了民主党派发展组织的一些思想问题，进一步了解了民主党派的性质、历史、作用和前途。4.检讨了过去对统战工作不重视或认为统战工作只是统战部与少数领导同志的事的思想，明确了今后工作的任务，增强了对统战工作的信心。"}],"contents":[{"id":"798bba61f4","type":"paragraph","text":"七月六日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a90ae50d78"},{"id":"91d9560b03","type":"paragraph","text":"此件很好，发各中央局，并转分局，省市区党委参考，并请仿照办理，加强全党的统一战线工作。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a90ae50d78"},{"id":"9741ecb4f2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a90ae50d78"},{"id":"fc0589c347","type":"title","text":"中央转发北京市委关于统战会议情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a90ae50d78"}],"page":{"id":"02359e78f9","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a90ae50d78","start":423,"end":423}}}},"__N_SSG":true}